title: Grateful Dead Live at Harding Theater on 1971-11-07
description:
Set I
Truckin'
Brown Eyed Women
Beat It On Down The Line
Hideaway
Sugaree
Jack Straw
Tennessee Jed
Cumberland Blues
El Paso
Big Railroad Blues
Comes A Time
Mexicali Blues
One More Saturday Night
Set II
Ramble On Rose
Me & Bobby McGee
Loser
Sugar Magnolia
Dark Star >
Drums >
The Other One >
Me & My Uncle >
The Other One
Deal
Brokedown Palace,
Playing In The Band
Casey Jones
Not Fade Away >
Goin' Down The Road Feeling Bad >
Not Fade Away
E: Johnny B. Goode
E: Uncle John's Band


Comment
New Riders Of The Purple Sage opened
FM broadcast KSFX-San Francisco
Monitor issues throughout the first set

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Ron "Pigpen" McKernan - Hammond B3, Harmonica
Keith Godchaux - Piano
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
